    • Method Detail

      • createURI

        public static URI createURI(String uri)
        Create a URI object percent escaping as necessary. This means that reserved characters that could delimit a URI component must already be escaped if they are not intended as component delimiters. This allows the URI to be parsed into components with optional escaping. This method will not double escape characters in the URI.
        Parameters:
        uri - the URI as a string.
        Returns:
        the URI.

      • generate

        public void generate(String tagName,
            Appendable sb,
            boolean xhtml)
              throws IOException
        Generate link tag. Includes all attributes. This does not include an end tag. It is up to the caller to close the opening tag.
        Parameters:
        sb - the buffer.
        tagName - the tag name.
        xhtml - if content should be xhtml compatible.
        Throws:
        IOException - if an IO error occurs.
